data.meta_description:
26 likes, 0 comments - tennishallofame on September 30, 2023: "Daniel Nestor of Canada 🇨🇦 is making his second ballot appearance as a 2024 nominee! 

A few accomplishments on Nestor's resume include ⬇️
▪️Former doubles world No. 1 
▪️12 major titles in doubles and mixed doubles
▪️91 career titles
▪️First ATP player to win 1000 career doubles matches

Want to help him get into the International Tennis Hall of Fame? Vote now!

🔗: Link in bio | #ITHFVote".
